simulator.Rd

simulator

simulator(Nind = 50, Ngen = 50, muG = 0, sigmaG = 1, muE = 0,
  sigmaE = 1, Elim = 10, seedlings = 4, dispersal = 1,
  viability_deterministic = TRUE)

Arguments

Nind

int. Number of individuals
Ngen

int. Number of generations
muG

double. Mean of genetic values
sigmaG

double. Variance of genetic values
muE

double. Mean of environmental values
sigmaE

double. Variance of environmental values
Elim

double. Environmental gradient size
seedlings

int. Number of seedlings per cell
dispersal

int. Dispersal distance in cells
viability_deterministic

bool. Deterministic or probabilistic vaibility

Value

A data frame.

Examples


simulator()
